// AS_GFX_[EffectName].1.fx - Graphics/Post-Processing Effect Template (Mode C: Filter)
// Replace [EffectName] with your effect name (e.g., "CompositionGuides")
//
// GFX shaders are filters that process the existing image.
// They do NOT include position/scale by default.
// They should show depth-aware compositing and can use multi-pass techniques.

/**
 * AS_GFX_[EffectName].1.fx - [Brief Description]
